# QuadAnimationSystem  (sbx)

## Purpose
Sole writer of QuadComponent. Each frame, for every entity carrying a SpinComponent and a
QuadComponent, advances the spin's accumulated time (scaled by the DebugControls animation-speed
multiplier when present, otherwise 1.0) and recomputes the quad's transform (anchor + optional
orbit, rotation about z, scale, layer from anchor.z) and colour (constant base colour, or an
animated cycle when m_ColorCycleSpeed is non-zero).

## Input Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| DebugControlsSingletonComponent | read | Optional animation-speed multiplier; defaults to 1.0 when absent |
| SpinComponent | write | Read for parameters; accumulated time advanced in place |
| QuadComponent | write | Transform and colour recomputed each frame |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| SpinComponent | write | m_Elapsed advanced by the (scaled) frame delta |
| QuadComponent | write | m_Transform and m_Color recomputed from the spin parameters |
